{
  "stem": "21648.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was OK, the young girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German young fellas, old fellas, I don't know was raping them, was kill-- starting to kill one by one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They raped them, and then they shot them to death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they make their parents to stay and watch what they doing to their children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It-- it seemed unbearable to talk about these things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he make put us in yellow patches we was wear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they make the ghetto for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they make rations-- rations for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then what they did [SOBBING] before I went to ghetto, my girlfriend was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I walked with her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[CRYING] I don't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The German was working, and they had their rifles with that sticks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said to her, you Communist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he killed her with the baby [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't talk about these things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then before the ghetto, they took 6-- 700 children what they could work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they put a sign on them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they put a bottle of milk and a piece of bread, and they drove them over the city, and they should scream and holler, Stalin gave us bread!",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Stalin gave us food!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then they took them and they put them a life in the graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[CRYING] It's unbearable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You can't talk about those things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they was-- what-- we wasn't used-- we was used to a luxury life in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they came, everything was in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to go shopping as-- in a line and food was very hard, but it was a life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't kill nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They do nothing to-- to the Jews except [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
